PrecisRegulations Amending the PROOF OF ORIGIN OF IMPORTED GOODS REGULATIONS to the extent that, in addition to a Certificate of Origin, goods originating in ISRAEL which have undergone minor processing within U.S. territory must be accompanied by a Declaration of Minor Processing in order to retain their preferential tariff status.
